OL,3,CGuernsey property prices drop slightly
OL,4,Cbut rent increases
OL,6,FThe average purchase price of a local
OL,7,Fmarket property in Guernsey has
OL,8,Fdropped slightly to #587,673.
OL,10,FThat is 2.2% lower than the same time
OL,11,Flast year, fuelled by sellers offering
OL,12,Fbigger discounts on advertised prices.
OL,14,FThe number of new buildings and homes
OL,15,Foverall sold on the local market went
OL,16,Fdown compared to the second quarter of
OL,17,F2023.
