OL,3,CGuernsey property prices drop slightly
OL,4,Cbut rent increases
OL,6,FHowever, tenants saw their rent
OL,7,Fincrease on local market properties to
OL,8,Fan average of nearly #2,000 a month,
OL,9,F5.7% more than the same time in 2023
OL,10,Fand nearly double the price they paid
OL,11,Ffive years ago.
OL,13,FEconomic expert Richard Hemans says:
OL,14,F"The housing market is still very weak
OL,15,Fwith both prices and transactions
OL,16,Fdeclining. However, there are no signs
OL,17,Fof distress and it seems that the
OL,18,Fmarket continues to normalise after an
OL,19,Funprecedented period of activity
OL,20,Fduring the COVID years.
