OL,3,CGuernsey property prices drop slightly
OL,4,Cbut rent increases
OL,6,F"Rent remains relatively unaffordable
OL,7,Ffor those who are not property owners,
OL,8,Fconsuming a painful 55% of average
OL,9,Fearnings and leaving little money
OL,10,Favailable for other expenditure."
OL,12,FReflecting on how much flats,
OL,13,Fbungalows and houses will now set
OL,14,Fsomeone back in Guernsey, there is
OL,15,Fstill marked increase on purchase
OL,16,Fprices across all sectors compared to
OL,17,F2019 and 2014.
